# AutoInsight

LLM-driven AutoML agentic system with a FastAPI + React interface.

## Structure
- `AutoInsight/` — core pipeline (LangGraph, agents, tools)
- `autoinsight-ui/` — web interface (FastAPI backend + Vite/React frontend)

## Setup
See `AutoInsight/README` and `autoinsight-ui/README.md` for instructions.